Third-party Notices
===================

Third-party mods, resource packs, shader packs, tools, libraries, and referenced
or derived content retain their original upstream licenses. Referencing,
describing, bundling, or modifying such content in this repository does not
relicense it under this project's license.

Known third-party parts:

- @bro-know-my/packwiz: MIT
  - Installed tool: global npm package `@bro-know-my/packwiz`
  - Purpose: developer tool for maintaining packwiz-style modpack metadata
  - Source project: https://github.com/bro-know-my-org/BroKnowMyPackwiz
  - The tool is not vendored in this repository and should not be shipped as part of the modpack runtime.

- TACZ Create Armorer Koei
